.name
VirusX
.author
Steve Tibbett 
.source
Includes source in C.
.description
A boot sector virus check program that runs in the background and
automatically checks all inserted disks for a nonstandard boot sector.
Such disks can optionally have their boot sector rewritten to remove the
virus.  
